data.definition: A large ball of hot gas in space that shines, like the Sun, or a shape with points.
The large, round object that shines in the night sky and orbits the Earth.
The planet we live on; also, the soil or ground.
A big ball of ice and rock that flies through space and often has a long, bright tail.
To move in a curved path around a larger object, like the Earth orbits the sun.
